[The number of reported fatal AES cases in Bihar was 142 in Muzaffarpur district as of 8 Jul 2019; the report above indicates that there are 47 deaths and the report below indicates that at least 109 children have died. The reason for the discrepancies is not apparent. - Mod.TY]

